{"tid":114197,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[多字少圖] 兩個人的北京4日快閃跨年之旅","createTime":"2017-02-09T14:44:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-27T18:43:40.000Z","uid":45774,"like":9,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eca96f4a38105f817ee6e45077c9143541795f8a","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T14:44:03.000Z","msg":"完成左我篇東京遊記<br />\n事不宜遲開始寫我另一個旅程--北京<br />\n<br />\n如果大家想睇東京篇遊記，可以click下面條link<br />\n《一個人的6日東京及近郊之旅》<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/101577/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/101577/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n點解會去北京呢個地方呢？<br />\n事緣係想睇雪，但又搶唔到hk express megasale機票<br />\n所以一怒之下就拍板去北京！<br />\n反正因爲我同友人都未去過北京<br />\n當係周圍行下<br />\n<br />\n事先聲明<br />\n因爲12月中小弟去完泰國之後就病左<br />\n一路病到北京出發當日都仲要食藥<br />\n所以無乜點做資料搜集<br />\n都係靠係飛機上面先plan<br />\n所以呢個trip都比較休閒同大路<br />\n如果你期待好似我上一篇東京之行咁多新發現<br />\n我勸你地可以返回上一頁<br />\n<br />\n先比大家有關呢個旅程嘅資料啦<br />\n<br />\n29/12/2016 - 2/1/2017<br />\n<br />\n<ins>開支 = HKD2700</ins><br />\n機票：HKD1250 (香港航空)<br />\n住宿：HKD950 (Agoda 4星級酒店連自助早餐)<br />\n洗費：HKD1500 (含交通、門票、飲食)<br />\n<br />\n我必須承認洗得太多，皆因住宿個度無住平野<br />\n<br />\n行程<br />\n第一日：抵達北京&mdash;&mdash;頤和園&mdash;&mdash;海底撈<br />\n第二日：南山滑雪場&mdash;&mdash;鳥巢、水立方&mdash;&mdash;王府井大街<br />\n第三日：八達嶺長城&mdash;&mdash;九門小吃&mdash;&mdash;什刹海 烤肉季<br />\n第四日：升國旗&mdash;&mdash;便宜坊烤鴨&mdash;&mdash;故宮&mdash;&mdash;天安門廣場&mdash;&mdash;東來順羊肉火鍋 <br />\n第五日：回到香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n航班於29號上午7點40分出發<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Za/lF/ZalFebHw7R2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FZa%2FlF%2FZalFebHw7R2h.jpg&h=2fbd107d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n比大家望望HK airline個飛機餐啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/dn/pe/dnpeuY1QqERp.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fdn%2Fpe%2FdnpeuY1QqERp.jpg&h=4aab1e4b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n另外仲有個係炒麵 (我個fd話完全無味)<br />\n相對蛋就比較正常，雖然飽肚感就低d"},{"pid":"53715b400553b1a1b8ed018e84ef1199475c32fb","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:08:50.000Z","msg":"一到步，攞埋行李<br />\n第一時間就走去地鐵站買張&quot;一卡通&quot;<br />\n所謂&quot;一卡通&quot;即係我地香港八達通<br />\n可以搭地鐵、巴士、於便利店購物都用到<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/eI/uJ/eIuJl6DhCnGH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FeI%2FuJ%2FeIuJl6DhCnGH.jpg&h=078ded48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一張卡20蚊按金<br />\n每次充值都要10蚊起，及10蚊 10蚊咁上<br />\n我就直接比左張100蚊搞掂曬所有野算<br />\n<br />\n呢張卡真係好划算<br />\n因爲按金係可以退<br />\n而且搭車會平d<br />\n一定要買！<br />\n<br />\n然後就搭機場快綫出市區<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/wl/Lo/wlLo2ecWQCX3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fwl%2FLo%2FwlLo2ecWQCX3.jpg&h=f9c3bf0e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n個列車如果多d位就好......<br />\n因爲印象中好似得4卡<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/gT/Eg/gTEg1GNIau6l.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FgT%2FEg%2FgTEg1GNIau6l.jpg&h=6582c5c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/4j/f0/4jf0tweGQVcT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F4j%2Ff0%2F4jf0tweGQVcT.jpg&h=e5512113&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n沿路都係呢d景色<br />\n全部都係枯葉<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/X5/Ff/X5FfEpujsqBA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FX5%2FFf%2FX5FfEpujsqBA.jpg&h=ee36d137&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一到步，放低行李<br />\n就即刻出去覓食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n因爲個陣已經係兩點嘅事<br />\n<br />\n我本身係打算去大碗居食炸醬麵<br />\n但我行左幾個字都搵唔到<br />\n一怒之下求其行左入去一間麻辣燙<br />\n<br />\n自己夾餸然後去秤 段磅計<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/3z/sO/3zsOX8KkMvMc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F3z%2FsO%2F3zsOX8KkMvMc.jpg&h=a416cfa5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我夾左27蚊人仔<br />\n<br />\n伏野黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以爲係平時食開個d麻辣燙<br />\n但呢度呢間就落好多麻醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人係超級唔中意麻醬<br />\n再加上連辣味都無埋<br />\n我個刻真係想屌出聲<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/v8/EM/v8EMXIDRVdls.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fv8%2FEM%2Fv8EMXIDRVdls.jpg&h=422746f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n入面有豆腐、芽菜、午餐肉、海帶、豆卜、娃娃菜等<br />\n都係好索汁嘅配料，結果索曬麻醬......<br />\n<br />\n然後就利用&quot;一卡通&quot;前往頤和園"},{"pid":"501c186416e42ace64df05af25b0114bd58c3c96","tid":114197,"uid":3358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:17:50.000Z","msg":"北方人係好撚鐘意麻醬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n自問鐘意麻醬都頂唔順"},{"pid":"977fdfb9429d9ee320568ae2a542b25c0e680a66","tid":114197,"uid":1567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:43:48.000Z","msg":"1250+950+1500=2700?"},{"pid":"20aa1e970c63c343ac51a33d3a8ab14e74a90656","tid":114197,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:46:09.000Z","msg":"見到碗野就唔開胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e6bc584711de51f0003cdedd9990e7d1951b055","tid":114197,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T15:47:51.000Z","msg":"賊都你都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:4年前去過"},{"pid":"f269ecca198544272563e382641eb013cd71a054","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1250+950+1500=2700?</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 手快快打錯"},{"pid":"79fef96914b9803816acb4f9fd81d7bb3257ee10","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:24:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><br />\n<ins>開支 = HKD<span style=\"color: red;\">3700</span></ins><br />\n機票：HKD1250 (香港航空)<br />\n住宿：HKD950 (Agoda 4星級酒店連自助早餐)<br />\n洗費：HKD1500 (含交通、門票、飲食)<br />\n</blockquote>"},{"pid":"34e31705f79a5bb5fd5eb92be0787b9490c7a391","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:25:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>賊都你都去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申:4年前去過</blockquote><br />\n我又唔係點怕<br />\n我自己幾中意周圍去<br />\n希望趁後生可以去多d唔同地方"},{"pid":"33f07781355fa08ef63a5748982dbf56963d1bb0","tid":114197,"uid":47971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T16:55:30.000Z","msg":"支持 上個po我都有睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b881a5d25599a0d81a298e5f673292cd4432e256","tid":114197,"uid":75552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知自由行交通方唔方便 淨係去過2次交流團 都好想自己去下 好掛住啲老胡同"},{"pid":"2a319f11ea2888d7a5936ae43ab305951316f40c","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:31:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 想知自由行交通方唔方便 淨係去過2次交流團 都好想自己去下 好掛住啲老胡同</blockquote><br />\n北京交通算好方便<br />\n地鐵配套其實都已經好發達<br />\n市區基本上都通曬地鐵"},{"pid":"04041fb0592e5e23aa1b3e1d4a7b0fb77d265860","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-09T17:31:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>支持 上個po我都有睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n多謝曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bcfd5add4441b5bca70e387119b6e3066dec9c4","tid":114197,"uid":62757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T01:19:59.000Z","msg":"留名支持"},{"pid":"10d119edd5a495a736b250075fac24254380e8b8","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:00:42.000Z","msg":"要去頤和園<br />\n就要搭車去到北宮門站<br />\n一出站跟住指示牌行就得<br />\n<br />\n先買門票再行入去<br />\n門票價格旺季30蚊，淡季20蚊<br />\n旺季：4月1日至10月31日<br />\n淡季：11月1日至次年3月31日<br />\n我去個陣係淡季，所以10蚊<br />\n10蚊!?唔係20蚊咩?<br />\n<br />\n北京絕大部分歷史景點都設有學生門票<br />\n而學生票(優惠票)一般都係正價票票價一半<br />\n包括故宮、動物園、頤和園、天安門、天壇等都設有優惠票<br />\n香港學生只需要係售票前講低話要優惠票，然後遞上學生証就得<br />\n<br />\n行到入去就見到蘇州街<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/LA/YL/LAYL4aA0Qbq4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FLA%2FYL%2FLAYL4aA0Qbq4.jpg&h=1e2ebe16&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/eE/mF/eEmF85X6FpZV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FeE%2FmF%2FeEmF85X6FpZV.jpg&h=2e5efb9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n湖面都結成冰<br />\n<br />\n沿路行上去都係好似公園咁<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/a7/Kc/a7KctvVw23Pq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fa7%2FKc%2Fa7KctvVw23Pq.jpg&h=3404360c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/4i/iX/4iiX8w6zZdRt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F4i%2FiX%2F4iiX8w6zZdRt.jpg&h=7f8bd011&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係最高處望落去....<br />\n景觀十分一般<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/KO/ID/KOIDVk5kFWZu.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FKO%2FID%2FKOIDVk5kFWZu.jpg&h=eab57057&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n一路慢慢行就行到宿雲簷城關<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/XM/Xt/XMXtqf31RjpE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FXM%2FXt%2FXMXtqf31RjpE.jpg&h=2b0f3cc3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/bK/18/bK18uYaFAKDW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FbK%2F18%2FbK18uYaFAKDW.jpg&h=a9640ff1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n成個湖面都係冰<br />\n超想行上去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n亦都去到好多人影相嘅船塢<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/lM/Cy/lMCyT3SFuX4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FlM%2FCy%2FlMCyT3SFuX4A.jpg&h=4cf7dc7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n日落開始，個天色都開始變<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/MK/Ie/MKIe3APtNY99.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FMK%2FIe%2FMKIe3APtNY99.jpg&h=7335ebcf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實你問我有咩特別<br />\n我真係答唔出<br />\n因爲呢度比我感覺純粹係一個環境清幽嘅大公園<br />\n所以呢我個人覺得黎唔黎都無所謂<br />\n不過如果慕頤和園呢個名黎都可以嘅"},{"pid":"fbfa4626c9148d9bacbb938a420aee0b6bbad2ba","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>要去頤和園<br />\n就要搭車去到北宮門站<br />\n一出站跟住指示牌行就得<br />\n<br />\n....................<br />\n<br />\n其實你問我有咩特別<br />\n我真係答唔出<br />\n因爲呢度比我感覺純粹係一個環境清幽嘅大公園<br />\n所以呢我個人覺得黎唔黎都無所謂<br />\n不過如果慕頤和園呢個名黎都可以嘅</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n當然黎呢度最主要原因當然係歷史價值為主"},{"pid":"4dd352c7bf451e4d7db2e78c4ce957c79c82c01d","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-10T05:44:29.000Z","msg":"行到5點左右就搭地鐵出番市區<br />\n<br />\n個日超級凍，所以我地首選都係打邊爐<br />\n因爲平時好少上大陸，所以一直都未試過海底撈<br />\n今次就順便試下海底撈<br />\n<br />\n要等一個鐘，所以我地都選擇去出面商場行下<br />\n<br />\n夜晚王府井大街都算熱鬧<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/n0/mb/n0mb2sAVGrdk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fn0%2Fmb%2Fn0mb2sAVGrdk.jpg&h=41547595&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n比多張日頭你地<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/x2/fQ/x2fQrV4rU0Z8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fx2%2FfQ%2Fx2fQrV4rU0Z8.jpg&h=04e5757e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都真係好繁華<br />\n有Apple Store、Gap、Zara、Burberry呢d比較知名品牌<br />\n可見其國際化<br />\n<br />\n呢部橙汁機係我係新東安商場見到<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/1x/G8/1xG8Ht0AJgS0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F1x%2FG8%2F1xG8Ht0AJgS0.jpg&h=1644a300&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n小弟大鄉里出城，覺得超級驚訝<br />\n因爲之前係荷蘭見過一次<br />\n但係亞洲就第一次見<br />\n<br />\n15蚊人仔一杯<br />\n我見有人買，部機用左7個橙整左一杯<br />\n就肉眼所見就無加水同糖精/糖漿<br />\n不過我無買到，因爲等陣去海底撈飲野好過<br />\n<br />\n行到咁上下就準備番去<br />\n途徑見到街頭雕塑<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/kX/uo/kXuoufUh953B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FkX%2Fuo%2FkXuoufUh953B.jpg&h=816e3581&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我本身係好辣者，所以湯底一定要揀麻辣(左)<br />\n而另外久聞海底撈番茄湯底(右)，所以叫左鴛鴦鍋<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/MA/OW/MAOWth2HobZm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FMA%2FOW%2FMAOWth2HobZm.jpg&h=dfd4eb5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n海底撈一直聲稱其番茄湯底係可以直接飲用<br />\n不加任何番茄精同d乜精乜精<br />\n個waiter都問我地要唔要試下<br />\n我就當然話ok<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/dq/23/dq236xBmDZqQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fdq%2F23%2Fdq236xBmDZqQ.jpg&h=2d557410&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nWaiter另外加左d蔥花<br />\n一飲....<br />\n果然係好濃郁番茄味<br />\n而且感覺係真係似平時用番茄煲湯個種味<br />\n我必須承認我飲左幾碗<br />\n<br />\n我地叫左肥牛、菜、薯仔、豆腐、麵、貝柱滑<br />\n係擺得好睇嘅<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Hc/wA/HcwAgasx0FRw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FHc%2FwA%2FHcwAgasx0FRw.jpg&h=fb9976f7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n你叫嘅麵其實係手拉麵<br />\n會即場拉比你睇<br />\n幾蚊一個麵，又有埋表演比你睇<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/iz/aW/izaWpSLwgGr0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2Fiz%2FaW%2FizaWpSLwgGr0.jpg&h=5e1d1f35&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後我地食左184蚊<br />\n人均￥92<br />\n價錢還可以，食物質素正常<br />\n服務態度太好<br />\n好到我多次話&quot;我們自己來就可以&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n呢個就係我地間酒店<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/hU/nX/hUnXaMZqjSRz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FhU%2FnX%2FhUnXaMZqjSRz.jpg&h=367be4b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n叫北京諾富特和平賓館<br />\n係連鎖企業，係香港都有旗下酒店<br />\n<br />\n間房比較亂，唔好介意<br />\n最平嘅房都已經好大<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/5S/GO/5SGOqQ9nm1U7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F5S%2FGO%2F5SGOqQ9nm1U7.jpg&h=cf2001f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/3e/4z/3e4zhNP0v9vQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F3e%2F4z%2F3e4zhNP0v9vQ.jpg&h=27e24bde&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a5d291e41583c47d8b527a0cd7384342d6517ed4","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T10:09:30.000Z","msg":"去到第二日<br />\n其實我對呢一日無乜太大興趣<br />\n完全係我朋友想去，然後我就幫佢搵資料<br />\n(無錯 每次同朋友去都係我自己一個搵資料plan行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> )<br />\n<br />\n今日日頭要進行嘅活動就係滑雪<br />\n實不相瞞，我係未滑過雪<br />\n所以我都好擔心<br />\n<br />\n我地選擇嘅滑雪場位於密雲縣 -- <span style=\"color: red;\">南山滑雪場</span><br />\n首先要去東直門交通樞紐站轉乘980快巴士<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/yN/OF/yNOFhICPYSlz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FyN%2FOF%2FyNOFhICPYSlz.jpg&h=c9d46106&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大概搭一個鐘左右就會到密雲縣<br />\n只要係太揚家園/密雲西大橋其中一個站落車就得<br />\n因爲要係呢兩個巴士站轉乘&quot;黑的&quot;<br />\n即係無牌的士<br />\n<br />\n以下呢個環境就係太揚家園<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/RY/G9/RYG95fWoCvN5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FRY%2FG9%2FRYG95fWoCvN5.jpg&h=4565a0f0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n無需要擔心無黑的<br />\n因爲d黑的一早排曬係巴士站隔離<br />\n一開始對方會開價￥40<br />\n記得講價 最起碼講到￥30先好上<br />\n我個陣講左15分鐘 結果最後￥25比我搭<br />\n<br />\n係車上面司機會問你洗唔洗去佢d朋友度租雪服<br />\n你自己選擇係滑雪場租or去司機朋友度租都得<br />\n但我穩鎮起見都係去滑雪場租<br />\n<br />\n去到滑雪場個門口<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/La/gH/LagHroUVmcPC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FLa%2FgH%2FLagHroUVmcPC.jpg&h=879c0454&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先我去接待處度話之前上網已經book左個package<br />\n閑日￥165/4hrs<br />\n但結果去到就話完全無record<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nok fine 既然黎到都要滑啦<br />\n結果就要當係散客即場買飛<br />\n￥150/2hrs ; 雪服￥40 ; Locker￥10<br />\n<br />\n比完錢就會比張儲值卡你<br />\n然後用卡攞雪服、滑雪用具<br />\n當卡一使用就開始計時<br />\n<br />\n我地首先係參觀環境先，並無即刻去滑<br />\n係一個平地練習場<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Xd/YA/XdYAt6Wpstan.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FXd%2FYA%2FXdYAt6Wpstan.jpg&h=79a64ba5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個場嘅重點<br />\n見到都驚<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/YG/KU/YGKUsBwrmkLW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FYG%2FKU%2FYGKUsBwrmkLW.jpg&h=c19879e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Tc/Ds/TcDsVzSW4Ms2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FTc%2FDs%2FTcDsVzSW4Ms2.jpg&h=8258d068&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢邊就係for初級人士使用<br />\n都有一定斜度<br />\n而我兩個鐘就係呢度渡過<br />\n有跌過有開心過<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/F1/jt/F1jtv2bHS2OM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FF1%2Fjt%2FF1jtv2bHS2OM.jpg&h=1983c4f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n黃昏時間咸蛋黃就出黎<br />\n但周圍都開始變得灰暗<br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/7k/Ao/7kAofjoRRgMF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2F7k%2FAo%2F7kAofjoRRgMF.jpg&h=b27f2133&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://storage.googleapis.com/files-as.myalbum.io/photo/1k0/Sy/h1/Syh1aYKZUMOP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstorage.googleapis.com%2Ffiles-as.myalbum.io%2Fphoto%2F1k0%2FSy%2Fh1%2FSyh1aYKZUMOP.jpg&h=7ce90984&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n利用同樣方法出番市區<br />\n記住要搭巴士出東直門就要係你落車個度嘅對面巴士站搭<br />\n通常都無位<br />\n另外滑雪場其實都有專車 不過每一各來回一班<br />\n所以就唔適合我啦"},{"pid":"8728e080d38b810666e8f96637faa39450478267","tid":114197,"uid":357,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48cbef76b718ce7178a022ae7d18e1e3b1ec3a66","tid":114197,"uid":45498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:25:45.000Z","msg":"睇雪去東京啦 痴撚線去支那，<br />\n上咗去就唔好返嚟，<br />\n記得吸多啲霧霾呀"},{"pid":"1b2cde00a34b9d1d47f49f99323d608e0961e05f","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T13:35:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>睇雪去東京啦 痴撚線去支那，<br />\n上咗去就唔好返嚟，<br />\n記得吸多啲霧霾呀</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n抱歉 我去完支那之後就去左東京<br />\n第一個貼已經有link<br />\n<br />\n香港空氣污染都好嚴重 <br />\n祝閣下個鼻早日失靈"},{"pid":"40155c5a1afbaaa5cb1fb5fb77737e1b37173d17","tid":114197,"uid":49316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T15:46:22.000Z","msg":"南山去過。仲住埋個乜柒雪屋<br />\n<br />\n中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8711de612bae72ccae714691582d004e9c10307f","tid":114197,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T00:14:22.000Z","msg":"對部支那橙汁機有d興趣<br />\n想問後尾有無買"},{"pid":"18cd479f072c0bf80bb316928be31f7fafa3128d","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T02:38:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>對部支那橙汁機有d興趣<br />\n想問後尾有無買</blockquote><br />\n我朋友有買到<br />\n話正正常常一杯鮮榨橙汁"},{"pid":"56c4eaa1d9410458e20ec2fe2bd87323abf4a7c3","tid":114197,"uid":45774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T02:38:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>南山去過。仲住埋個乜柒雪屋<br />\n<br />\n中伏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n居然住個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}